If you’re still ignoring UGC in 2025, just say you don’t like engagement 😌

UGC is created by real people; your customers, fans, and community sharing real experiences with your brand. It builds trust, boosts engagement, and drives conversions because people relate to people, not ads. 

In a world full of noise, UGC is what actually cuts through and connects.

— UGC Bolt
